{"tid":1363424,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"其實我地係唔係要幫下D真素人對抗譚香文呢","createTime":"2019-07-25T07:27:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-23T04:25:22.000Z","uid":4521,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"8609c1c0b399e39d60524cfbe6c1fd190eeaa79d","tid":1363424,"uid":4521,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T07:27:24.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">先利伸:永不相信譚香文</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n11月就黎到 好多人因為反送中而醒左決定出黎重政下政壇。<br />\n但係可惜現時政壇係比建制同泛民控制哂, 而今次真素人就只可以含淚埋下泛民堆<br />\n<br />\n但係，譚香文團隊搞左個反自己當選既PAGE出黎造反白區<br />\n但就不斷出現推區情況，到今日撞足咁多區仲不斷叫人聯絡佢<br />\n其實佢係咪想利呢D素人出黎幫自己向泛民報仇?<br />\n<br />\n譚香文呢個老狐狸真係私怨撚黎，佢會唔會搞咁多野出黎為香港心中有數。<br />\n<br />\n你可以唔信我，唔信泛民, 但連自己人連登仔都出左聲明。阻大家少少時間去思考下呢件事<br />\n我地真係仲要比政棍擺佈定自己救香港呢?<br />\n<br />\n【有關2019年香港區議會選舉協調工作之澄清聲明】<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1323489/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1323489/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"2de9aed8ac51d6ec7eeb45b4f9d91e7f97d5a0b6","tid":1363424,"uid":4521,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T07:29:08.000Z","msg":"PUSH"},{"pid":"7a866c151a2bf93539f1d3a1feb43305d123969b","tid":1363424,"uid":267365,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T04:25:22.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%e6%b8%af%e8%81%9e/article/20190822/s00001/1566476483485/%e3%80%90%e5%8d%80%e8%ad%b0%e6%9c%83%e9%81%b8%e8%88%89-emily-online%e3%80%91%e6%9b%89%e9%ba%97%e7%85%a7%e6%90%9e%e5%88%9d%e9%81%b8-%e5%8d%94%e8%aa%bf%e8%a6%8b%e8%ad%89%e4%ba%ba%e6%8c%87%e8%ad%9a%e9%a6%99%e6%96%87%e5%87%ba%e7%88%be%e5%8f%8d%e7%88%be\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25e6%25b8%25af%25e8%2581%259e%2Farticle%2F20190822%2Fs00001%2F1566476483485%2F%25e3%2580%2590%25e5%258d%2580%25e8%25ad%25b0%25e6%259c%2583%25e9%2581%25b8%25e8%2588%2589-emily-online%25e3%2580%2591%25e6%259b%2589%25e9%25ba%2597%25e7%2585%25a7%25e6%2590%259e%25e5%2588%259d%25e9%2581%25b8-%25e5%258d%2594%25e8